article: nine years after the united states vowed to shut down the money pipeline that finances terrorism , senior obama administration officials say they believe many millions of dollars are flowing largely unimpeded to extremist groups worldwide , and they have grown frustrated by frequent resistance from allies in the middle east , according to secret diplomatic dispatches .
